episodes.title: We went undercover to infiltrate a Yellow Deli Cult hotline
episodes.description:
Hello everyone I hope you enjoyed our cult investigation on the twelve tribes/Yellow deli cult which is a international cult that owns several unlisted farms. We do not condone harassment of the twelve tribes cult no matter how ridiculous they are. I want to thank Sam_Sizemore on Instagram for all his hard work with going under cover and making the music. 
Our team spent a lot of time on this and avoided putting a commercial in for our Patreon so if you want to help support future projects check out the patreon, we also have a lot of other cool things for patrons.
